    <tags>WPF MVVM MVVMLight ViewModel Converter MultiBinding Reflection</tags>
    <summary>
      ViewModelsMerger is a library for WPF, that helps you merge different ViewModels into one ViewModel at runtime.
      In cases where a View can have elements, controls or different regions that have different ViewModels,
      You don't need to change the DataContext in code every time for each part of the view,
      you just set one DataContext for the top parrent object that encompasses the different DataContexts (ViewModels)
      and Merge them into one ViewModel at RunTime.
    </summary>
